item.title: About
item.description:
About

Walk the Talk is a weekly conservative radio show that takes a look inside what's really going on in Nevada politics.  Join us every Saturday at 9:00am on AM720 KDWN where we discuss current issues with our special guests, callers, and the community. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WalkTheTalkwithMicheleFiore/

item.title: About Brigitte Gabriel
item.description:
About Brigitte Gabriel

Brigitte Gabriel is the Founder and President of Act for America. Ms. Gabriel is one of the leading national security experts in the world -providing information and analysis on the rise of Islamic terrorism. Ms. Gabriel lectures nationally and internationally about national security and current affairs.
